    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri dei et salvatori nostri Iesu Christi. Anno ab
                        incarnatione eiusdem millesimo centesimo sesto decimo, tercio <persName
                            ref="#people/127">Henrico</persName> imperante anno sesto, octavo idus
                        iulii, indictione nona. Dum esset <persName ref="#people/1261">Iohannes
                            Boitane</persName>
                        <rs key="#Missus_regis">misso</rs> domni Henrici <rs>imperatoris</rs> in
                            <rs>curte</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/1566"><geogName ref="#estates/1126"
                                >Celula</geogName></placeName> in loco, qui vocatur
                            <placeName>Runcus Domnicus</placeName> iusta <rs>stratha que vocatur
                            Cluza</rs>, et simul cum eo domnus <persName><name ref="Lanfrancus"
                                >Lanfrancus</name></persName>
                        <rs>monachus</rs> sicque <persName><name ref="Albericus"
                            >Albericus</name></persName>
                        <rs>vicecomitis</rs> seu <persName><name ref="Ildeprandus"
                                >Ildeprandus</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Ildeprandus">Ildeprandi</name></persName> namque
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Severus">Severo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Albertus/Candidus">Alberto
                            Candidus</name></persName>, <persName><name>Azo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Golfero</name></persName> et <rs>presbiter</rs>
                        <persName><name>Gianellus</name></persName> de <rs>castro</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/1575">Gipso</placeName> et
                                <persName><name>Ragimundus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Sandoni</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Tetelmus</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name>Gaurini</name></persName> de <rs>vico</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/1583">Petrosa</placeName> et alii plures, in
                        presentia suprascriptorum hominum venerunt hominibus habitatores in castro
                        Gipso, quorum nomina <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        de <persName><name ref="Ioseph">Ioseph</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Albertus/Perdutus">Albertus, qui vocatur
                            Perduto</name></persName>, et <persName><name ref="Constantinus"
                                >Constantinus</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Constantinus">Constantini</name></persName>. Fecerunt finem et
                        perpetuam transactionem pro ipsis et eorum consortes in manu prelibati
                        Iohannis misso imperiali vice aecclesie <rs>monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/47"
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">sancti Silvestri</orgName>
                        sito <placeName ref="#places/15">Nonantule</placeName> de omnibus illis
                        rebus territoriis, que ispi dicebant infra pertinentiis curte <placeName
                            ref="#places/2480"><geogName ref="#estates/1127"
                            >Ragigose</geogName></placeName> ex datione hominum <rs>comitipse</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/125">Matilde</persName>, qui ipsis dicebant eis date
                        essent per <rs>wardam</rs>
                        <rs>roce</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/1576">Gipsadelli</placeName>. Quas iam dicta
                        comitipsa Matilda ante eorum dationem per cartam proprietatis dedit in
                        predicta ecclesia sancti Silvestri in restauratione thesauri, quem ipsa
                        tulit suprascripte aecclesie, et nec <rs>abbas</rs> suprascripti monasterii
                        nec alius suus <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missus</rs>
                        concessit neque confirmavit in <rs>dactione</rs>, quem fecerunt suprascripti
                        homines Matilde in predictis hominibus Gipsi. Et si suprascriptam
                        transactionem non observaverint, incidant in penam et bannum imperatoris. Et
                        in suprascriptam penam promiserunt dare et conducere omne <rs>redditum</rs>
                        <rs>blavis</rs> de iam dicta terra secundum consuetudinem loci ad
                            <rs>hospicium</rs>
                        <placeName>Lavini</placeName>. Et si in aliquo tempore ostendunt iusta legem
                        habere pertinentiam, in suprascriptis rebus observetur eis. Omnes
                        suprascritpi homines rogati sunt testes. In dei nomine ego + <persName><name
                                ref="Albertus">Albertus</name></persName>
                        <rs>notarius</rs> scripsi hec.</ab>
